On 01/01/1916 near Etain.
A vehicle was destroyed by Sergent Marc Leclercq of Esc 108.
Sergent Marc Leclercq was flying a Farman F.40.

On 01/01/1916 near StMihiel.
A Albatros C.II of FA 16 was brought down by Sous Lieutenant Jean Pregermain of Esc 37.
The pilot was killed in action
Sous Lieutenant Jean Pregermain was flying a Nieuport 11.C1.

On 01/01/1916 near Perenchies.
A Albatros C.II of FA 7 was brought down by Major James Merstun of No 29 Squadron RFC.
The pilot was killed in action
Major James Merstun was flying a Airco D.H.2.
